{"tid":2077564,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分手之後唔敢再去某個地方嘅你","createTime":"2020-06-24T11:20:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T19:29:15.000Z","uid":186374,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ea4185960f03b0537402a933d0b9c0297a83a44","tid":2077564,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:20:08.000Z","msg":"要幾耐之後先可以如常咁去一個地方然後無特別感覺?<br />\n<br />\n年幾之後重遊舊地 個心有少少隱隱作痛<br />\n<br />\n但係其實又唔係話仲鐘意佢 只係覺得痛<br />\n<br />\n佢其實已經唔重要 <br />\n<br />\n就好似 其實我係比刀吉 比槍射 定比拳頭打 都唔重要<br />\n<br />\n重點係我身上多左道傷疤 傷口愈合緊 但會痛<br />\n<br />\n我想好好愛下一個"},{"pid":"507c09d9362a445c28cc6119bdab2a6488eb5e81","tid":2077564,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:21:22.000Z","msg":"未試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9cbbde3214827f92651369a5a5d32061ae1df6d","tid":2077564,"uid":73349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:23:17.000Z","msg":"去多幾次就麻木"},{"pid":"5c859e2aee12eebb3e0758f7bfc42d5cc398d4b9","tid":2077564,"uid":101650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"梅窩銀礦灣沙灘<br />\n<br />\n都十幾年無去過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cf45348993d599d795198ef4d3ac451ee0a513","tid":2077564,"uid":186374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c859e2aee12eebb3e0758f7bfc42d5cc398d4b9","tid":2077564,"uid":101650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:24:40.000Z","msg":"梅窩銀礦灣沙灘<br />\n<br />\n都十幾年無去過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:25:19.000Z","msg":"十幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無帶現任去下?"},{"pid":"8